itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway sit down with actor Jaleel White to discuss his new podcast embracing what it was like being a child star playing Steve Urkel on tv to transitioning into other roles as an adult. He also chats about the time he met Michael Jackson and wasn’t invited to Neverland Ranch.
